{"tid":696172,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[留意撚] 成日幫housemate執手尾求助","createTime":"2018-06-09T23:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T22:06:11.000Z","uid":123933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4c178c5f840047e53ce93242258079609fc5c9","tid":696172,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T23:32:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟係留學生，宜家已經同呢班housemate住咗一年，下年仲要住多一年。<br />\n<br />\n大家bonding 都非常好，純粹係無手尾，咁我平時都會直接執埋佢地手尾。<br />\n<br />\n但有時真係頂唔順，例如開完啲包裝亂劈，洗野成日洗完都係油，煮完野整污糟唔抹等等，一次半次係無所謂，但係當差唔多每日都係咁就真係好辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n我其實講又講過，勸又勸過，鬧又鬧過，咩都做過晒，但都係無用。<br />\n<br />\n宜家諗緊下年點樣可以令大家都學識點樣做野有手尾，希望可以集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c66820070b20a21516e586083de6be0e3e3e8d0","tid":696172,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T23:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b62053db998c6a79440e67a347c3d78e5499459","tid":696172,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T23:33:28.000Z","msg":"留學撚*<br />\ntopic 打錯自膠<img src=\"/assets/face